## Deliverable — **Mood / style bible image prompt** (for alignment boards)

```text
Mood board, 3x3 grid, stylized 3D martial arts training hall, stick figure fighter silhouette center, warm wood floor cool walls, dramatic but readable lighting, cel-shaded OR PBR-lite clean, no text, no logo, cohesive palette hex swatches implied, John Stick art direction
Negative: photorealistic skin, clutter props, lens dirt, busy posters
```

## Deliverable — **Material spec snippet** (per surface)

```yaml
surface: dojo_floor_mat
workflow: metal_roughness
baseColor: "#..."
roughness: 0.55–0.75
metalness: 0
normal: optional 512
notes: avoid fine stripes; test at 15m camera distance
```

## Working with a non-expert user

Ask: **2 reference images** or **one film** for palette. If none: **ship default palette** + **one alt**.

## Anti-patterns

- **Per-asset** style drift between props and characters.
- Signing **post** without **off** switch for min-spec (§9.2.2).
